settings.graphqlSchema:
schema {
    query: Query
    mutation: Mutation
}

type Query {
    queryAsset(
        assetUniqueId: String
    ): FixedAsset
}

type Mutation {
    receiveAsset(
        assetUniqueId: String,
        description: String,
        acquisitionDate: String,
        location: String,
        manufacturer: String,
        vendor: String,
        model: String,
        serialNum: String,
        orgId: String): FixedAsset
    installAsset(
        assetUniqueId: String,
        description: String,
        acquisitionDate: String,
        location: String,
        manufacturer: String,
        vendor: String,
        model: String,
        serialNum: String,
        orgId: String,
        installDate: String): FixedAsset
    receiveInvoice(
        assetUniqueId: String,
        description: String,
        location: String,
        invoiceDate: String,
        orgId: String,
        invoicePrice: Float,
        vendor: String): FixedAsset
    faUpdate(
        assetUniqueId: String,
        description: String,
        purchasePrice: Float,
        location: String,
        model: String,
        orgId: String,
        installDate: String,
        invoiceDate: String,
        netBookValue: Float,
        serialNum: String): FixedAsset
    submitPO(
        assetUniqueId: String,
        description: String,
        purchasePrice: Float,
        location: String,
        vendor: String,
        orgId: String): FixedAsset
}

type FixedAsset {
    assetUniqueId: ID
    assetNum: String
    assetTag: String
    orgId: String
    siteId: String
    statusDate: String
    serialNum: String
    model: String
    purchasePrice: Float
    invoicePrice: Float
    netBookValue: Float
    owner: String
    vendor: String
    manufacturer: String
    value: String
    location: String
    acquisitionDate: String
    installDate: String
    invoiceDate: [String]
    retireDate: String
    status: String
    description: String
}
